Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
## Action BSFCY
Call AS_FCY(VALEUR) From DIVPAYE
If mkstat=2
 [M]FCY(INDIC) = VALEUR
 Affzo FCY(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_FCY(zc) From W1GENMPS
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_FCY(zc) From W1GENMPS
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_FCY(zc) From W1GENMPS
Gosub _AFF
